rest_of_day_open: It should be a quiet week as it is week until my money arrives.  I need to take my wife and her service dog to the dog trainer this week but that is it.  Weather wise it will be another humid, hot and muggy week.  If everything goes according to plan there will be no stress this week.
critical_positive: The other person was friendly and punctual.   She did not let the technical issue she was having interrupt our conversation and tried to keep the conversation flowing.   She was a good listener and seemed to follow the conversation very well.  Overall she was a very nice friendly conversational partner today.
critical_negative: She was hesitant to talk sometimes, preferring to listen.  This meant I carried more than 50 percent of the conversation. She also seem unsure of what to do vis a vis, being asked questions about where she was from.   She sometimes seemed to be afraid of being caught out and trapped in some manner.  But that could have been because of the video feed being so bad and intermittent.

rest_of_day_open: I'm planning to plant more plants in my garden, I'll invite some friends to come over this weekend, I'll cook some interesting Turkish recipes and desserts, I'll take my dog to the park, I'll continue writing poems and working on my novel, I'll take a swim in the pool every day.
critical_positive: Everything went well with the conversation, I found out new things, I liked the personality of my conversation partner and I felt empathy and sympathy for  my partner's family situation, I appreciated the fact that my partner shared so much personal information with me, it was a very interesting conversation.
critical_negative: Everything went well, except...I wish my partner didn't have to talk too much about or focus too much on the political subject. I respect everybody's view point and I believe everybody has a right to speak and express their opinion, however this time I felt it was too much attention offered to the politics which happens that I'm not such a big fan of.
